<br>
Average DPS 68 without effects of procs.<br>
<br>
I then took the log file and replaced slashed by elemental mastery with slashes soandso for 143 points of damage; and same for the stun proc for 80 points.  I purposefully omitted the fists of ixiblat proc since there was a shaman pet which was using them and it would have overly inflated the DPS.  <br>
<br>
This replace allowed the log parser to handle the best case scenario of the procs.  With the procs in there was an interesting issue that came up.  The golems are 60+, spiders/crawlers are &lt;60.  The DPS for spiders/crawlers was around 90-95 DPS, for the golems it was still average 68 DPS; the procs do not land on them thus a decent chunk of pet damage is lost.<br>
<br>
The problem is that epic is too low to land spells on the high level MOBs and thus is left with only melee to do the damage.<br>
<br>
This issue needs to be addressed.<br>
